//just a sample of even or odd with python

x = int(input("enter x")          //as x takes value in the shell/pychorm
r = x%2                          //modules is represented with '%' symbol

If r==0:
   print("even") 

else:
   print("odd") 



print("Bye")                  //this line is not exhiguted with 'if' but printed in the shell







